                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Brezza:</span> ₹8.69L - ₹13.98L ex-showroom ● CNG variant (~₹9.6L)</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Sonet:</span> ₹8.00L - ₹15.74L ex-showroom depending on engine/trim (1.2L petrol MT to diesel AT)</li>
                </ul>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Takeaway:</span> Pricing brackets overlap significantly. Brezza typically costs less in petrol variants, while Sonet offers broader engine/gearbox diversity, including diesel AT.</p>

