                <h2 class="subheading">Final Verdict</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Choose the Brezza</span> for its <span class="font-weight-700">mild-hybrid efficiency</span>, <span class="font-weight-700">CNG option</span>, trustworthy <span class="font-weight-700">after-sales network</span>, and practicality for everyday city driving.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Opt for the Sonet</span> if you want a <span class="font-weight-700">turbo-diesel/petrol choice</span>, love <span class="font-weight-700">premium tech</span> (like ventilated seats and Bose audio), and don't mind paying a bit more for features and refinement.</li>
                </ul>

